Charles Wallace Roddy-Foster was born was born in Absarokee, MT on July 19th. He lives with his parents in Missoula, MT and spends a lot of time with his extended family.  He responds to many names including but not limited to "Char Char", "Charlie-Pie", and "Sweet Boy."  He gives excellent cuddles and enjoys long walks on the beach. With a taste for the finer things, he is a bit of a picky eater but loves carrots and ice cream.   